{"lang": "zh_TW", "eventid": "act34side", "eventName": "生路", "entryType": "ACTIVITY", "storyCode": "BP-1", "avgTag": "行動後", "storyName": "第一次接觸", "storyInfo": "斯卡蒂與幽靈鯊帶領博士參觀城市，執政官克萊門莎單獨會晤了歌蕾蒂婭。艾麗妮偶遇海巡隊，參與調查資料分析師失蹤的案子。\n", "storyList": [{"id": 0, "prop": "HEADER", "attributes": {"key": "title_test", "is_skippable": "true", "fit_mode": "BLACK_MASK"}}, {"id": 1, "prop": "Blocker", "attributes": {"a": 1.0, "r": 0.0, "g": 0.0, "b": 0.0, "fadetime": 0.0, "block": "true"}}, {"id": 2, "prop": "stopmusic", "attributes": {}}, {"id": 3, "prop": "Dialog", "attributes": {}}, {"id": 4, "prop": "Background", "attributes": {"image": "51_g1_beaconsquare", "screenadapt": "coverall"}}, {"id": 5, "prop": "Delay", "attributes": {"time": 1.0}}, {"id": 6, "prop": "Blocker", "attributes": {"a": 0.0, "r": 0.0, "g": 0.0, "b": 0.0, "fadetime": 1.0, "block": "true"}}, {"id": 7, "prop": "playMusic", "attributes": {"intro": "$warm_intro", "key": "$warm_loop", "volume": 0.6}}, {"id": 8, "prop": "Delay", "attributes": {"time": 2.0}}, {"id": 9, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "m", "name": "char_263_skadi#5", "duration": 1.0}}, {"id": 10, "prop": "Delay", "attributes": {"time": 2.0}}, {"id": 11, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "博士，你誤以為我們剛才參觀的建築是博物館了對吧？你看那些儀器的眼神很像在欣賞什麼展品。", "name": "斯卡蒂"}, "figure_art": "char_263_skadi#5"}, {"id": 12, "prop": "Dialog", "attributes": {}}, {"id": 13, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "m", "focus": "n"}}, {"id": 14, "prop": "Decision", "attributes": {"options": "這已經是我誤認成博物館的第三幢建築了。", "values": "1"}, "targetLine": {"option1": "line15"}}, {"id": 15, "prop": "Predicate", "attributes": {"references": "1"}, "endOfOpt": false}, {"id": 16, "prop": "Decision", "attributes": {"options": "建築內部的重力為什麼可以是顛倒的？;那些在立柱間自主穿行的水流是怎麼回事？;那片能讓我的手指扭曲變形的空間是什麼？", "values": "1;2;3"}, "targetLine": {"option1": "line17", "option2": "line17", "option3": "line17"}}, {"id": 17, "prop": "Predicate", "attributes": {"references": "1;2;3"}, "endOfOpt": false}, {"id": 18, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "m", "name": "char_263_skadi#5"}}, {"id": 19, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "有些原理，我也解釋不清。", "name": "斯卡蒂"}, "figure_art": "char_263_skadi#5"}, {"id": 20, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "這五年來，我們也錯過了很多新的科技進展。", "name": "斯卡蒂"}, "figure_art": "char_263_skadi#5"}, {"id": 21, "prop": "Dialog", "attributes": {}}, {"id": 22, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {}}, {"id": 23, "prop": "Decision", "attributes": {"options": "等等，前面的那座高塔……", "values": "1"}, "targetLine": {"option1": "line24"}}, {"id": 24, "prop": "Predicate", "attributes": {"references": "1"}, "endOfOpt": false}, {"id": 25, "prop": "Decision", "attributes": {"options": "城市的核心建築，是一座發射井？", "values": "1"}, "targetLine": {"option1": "line26"}}, {"id": 26, "prop": "Predicate", "attributes": {"references": "1"}, "endOfOpt": false}, {"id": 27, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "m", "name": "avg_1023_ghost2_1#1$1"}}, {"id": 28, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "你沒猜錯，博士，那是一座信標發射井。它的歷史已經不短了。", "name": "幽靈鯊"}, "figure_art": "avg_1023_ghost2_1#1$1"}, {"id": 29, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "m", "name": "char_263_skadi#5"}}, {"id": 30, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "鯊魚，你居然認識。", "name": "斯卡蒂"}, "figure_art": "char_263_skadi#5"}, {"id": 31, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "m", "name": "avg_1023_ghost2_1#1$1"}}, {"id": 32, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "很小的時候，父母帶我遊歷過本境，不少城市都存在類似的建築。", "name": "幽靈鯊"}, "figure_art": "avg_1023_ghost2_1#1$1"}, {"id": 33, "prop": "Dialog", "attributes": {}}, {"id": 34, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {}}, {"id": 35, "prop": "Decision", "attributes": {"options": "我以為阿戈爾人都是集體撫養長大的。", "values": "1"}, "targetLine": {"option1": "line36"}}, {"id": 36, "prop": "Predicate", "attributes": {"references": "1"}, "endOfOpt": false}, {"id": 37, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "m", "name": "char_263_skadi#3"}}, {"id": 38, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "我確實是，但鯊魚和她的血緣父母一直維持著很特別的關係。", "name": "斯卡蒂"}, "figure_art": "char_263_skadi#3"}, {"id": 39, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "m", "name": "avg_1023_ghost2_1#12$1"}}, {"id": 40, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "比起父母，更像是朋友吧。", "name": "幽靈鯊"}, "figure_art": "avg_1023_ghost2_1#12$1"}, {"id": 41, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "他們和公共養育所達成了奇妙的共識，基礎的撫養由公共養育所負責，但他們每接手一座城市的穹頂建設，就把我也帶過去。", "name": "幽靈鯊"}, "figure_art": "avg_1023_ghost2_1#12$1"}, {"id": 42, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "領著我滿城參觀、學習，甚至讓我也參與一點他們的工作……當然，大部分時候我還是住在公共養育所。", "name": "幽靈鯊"}, "figure_art": "avg_1023_ghost2_1#12$1"}, {"id": 43, "prop": "Dialog", "attributes": {}}, {"id": 44, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "m", "focus": "n"}}, {"id": 45, "prop": "Decision", "attributes": {"options": "說回來，這座信標發射井是用來做什麼的？", "values": "1"}, "targetLine": {"option1": "line46"}}, {"id": 46, "prop": "Predicate", "attributes": {"references": "1"}, "endOfOpt": false}, {"id": 47, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "m", "name": "avg_1023_ghost2_1#1$1"}}, {"id": 48, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "字面意思——負責發射信標，引領航道。", "name": "幽靈鯊"}, "figure_art": "avg_1023_ghost2_1#1$1"}, {"id": 49, "prop": "Dialog", "attributes": {}}, {"id": 50, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "m", "focus": "n"}}, {"id": 51, "prop": "Decision", "attributes": {"options": "一般的信標發射井不會有這樣的規模。;它所引領的究竟是什麼尺度下的航道？", "values": "1;2"}, "targetLine": {"option1": "line52", "option2": "line52"}}, {"id": 52, "prop": "Predicate", "attributes": {"references": "1;2"}, "endOfOpt": false}, {"id": 53, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "m", "name": "avg_1023_ghost2_1#10$1"}}, {"id": 54, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "大概三百年前，阿戈爾對海洋的開發就已經趨近完全。天然存在的各種能源得到利用，海床的每一道溝壑都在海圖上留有記錄。", "name": "幽靈鯊"}, "figure_art": "avg_1023_ghost2_1#10$1"}, {"id": 55, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "那時候，人們將目光投向了另一片閃爍著繁星的海洋。", "name": "幽靈鯊"}, "figure_art": "avg_1023_ghost2_1#10$1"}, {"id": 56, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "在當初的設想中，我們的艦隊，乃至我們的城市都將穿越那層本不應存在的界限，在阻隔層外點亮文明的火。", "name": "幽靈鯊"}, "figure_art": "avg_1023_ghost2_1#10$1"}, {"id": 57, "prop": "Dialog", "attributes": {}}, {"id": 58, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {}}, {"id": 59, "prop": "Decision", "attributes": {"options": "阻隔層外……", "values": "1"}, "targetLine": {"option1": "line60"}}, {"id": 60, "prop": "Predicate", "attributes": {"references": "1"}, "endOfOpt": false}, {"id": 61, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "m", "name": "avg_003_kalts_1#1$1"}}, {"id": 62, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "博士，保存者的判斷是準確的，克麗斯騰的壯舉在阿戈爾看來並非遙不可及。", "name": "凱爾希"}, "figure_art": "avg_003_kalts_1#1$1"}, {"id": 63, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "海洋國家與天空的距離，比我們一直以來想像的還要更近。", "name": "凱爾希"}, "figure_art": "avg_003_kalts_1#1$1"}, {"id": 64, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "m", "name": "avg_1023_ghost2_1#12$1"}}, {"id": 65, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "那時的人們抱著巨大的熱情做出了諸多嘗試——勘測與破解電子雲層，革新推進技術和材料技術，探索能適應太空環境的生命形式……", "name": "幽靈鯊"}, "figure_art": "avg_1023_ghost2_1#12$1"}, {"id": 66, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "我們眼前的信標發射井，便是當時的產物。", "name": "幽靈鯊"}, "figure_art": "avg_1023_ghost2_1#12$1"}, {"id": 67, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "至少在最初的設想中，它可以捕捉星空中最微小的訊號，也能在星圖的特定坐標上豎立永不熄滅的信標。", "name": "幽靈鯊"}, "figure_art": "avg_1023_ghost2_1#12$1"}, {"id": 68, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "信標之間，不計其數的微型浮游機械將以身軀連綴成路網，讓阿戈爾能在轉瞬間跨越悠遠的空間……至少，人們是如此設想的。", "name": "幽靈鯊"}, "figure_art": "avg_1023_ghost2_1#12$1"}, {"id": 69, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "m", "name": "char_263_skadi#5"}}, {"id": 70, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "鯊魚，你從來沒跟我說過這些。", "name": "斯卡蒂"}, "figure_art": "char_263_skadi#5"}, {"id": 71, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "m", "name": "avg_1023_ghost2_1#1$1"}}, {"id": 72, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "在陸地的時候，我清醒的時間很少，斯卡蒂。", "name": "幽靈鯊"}, "figure_art": "avg_1023_ghost2_1#1$1"}, {"id": 73, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "m", "name": "avg_1023_ghost2_1#10$1"}}, {"id": 74, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "但就在昨天，我做了一個夢，又一次夢見自己從鬥智場走入那段歷史。", "name": "幽靈鯊"}, "figure_art": "avg_1023_ghost2_1#10$1"}, {"id": 75, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "然後，我看見勞倫緹娜在跳舞。", "name": "幽靈鯊"}, "figure_art": "avg_1023_ghost2_1#10$1"}, {"id": 76, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "她的舞步從浪濤躍上星空，星塵追逐著她的裙襬。有一個聲音，從很遙遠很遙遠的地方傳來。那是萬物之主，萬物之主以歌聲回應她。", "name": "幽靈鯊"}, "figure_art": "avg_1023_ghost2_1#10$1"}, {"id": 77, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "宇宙沒有盡頭，想像無法窮盡，勞倫緹娜的舞步永不停止。", "name": "幽靈鯊"}, "figure_art": "avg_1023_ghost2_1#10$1"}, {"id": 78, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "m", "name": "avg_1023_ghost2_1#3$1"}}, {"id": 79, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "幽靈鯊閉上了眼睛，彷彿回到了那個夢裡。"}}, {"id": 80, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "m", "name": "char_263_skadi#4"}}, {"id": 81, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "唔……", "name": "斯卡蒂"}, "figure_art": "char_263_skadi#4"}, {"id": 82, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "m", "name": "avg_1023_ghost2_1#1$1"}}, {"id": 83, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "怎麼了？", "name": "幽靈鯊"}, "figure_art": "avg_1023_ghost2_1#1$1"}, {"id": 84, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "m", "name": "char_263_skadi#5"}}, {"id": 85, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "鯊魚，我在想像那個畫面。", "name": "斯卡蒂"}, "figure_art": "char_263_skadi#5"}, {"id": 86, "prop": "Dialog", "attributes": {}}, {"id": 87, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {}}, {"id": 88, "prop": "Decision", "attributes": {"options": "很美的夢，勞倫緹娜。;說不定真有那樣的時刻，勞倫緹娜。", "values": "1;2"}, "targetLine": {"option1": "line89", "option2": "line89"}}, {"id": 89, "prop": "Predicate", "attributes": {"references": "1;2"}, "endOfOpt": false}, {"id": 90, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "m", "name": "avg_1023_ghost2_1#12$1"}}, {"id": 91, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "在真正推開星海之門前，人們總試圖為阻隔層外的威脅做出更充分的準備……直到海嗣的出現打斷了這場漫長的夢。", "name": "幽靈鯊"}, "figure_art": "avg_1023_ghost2_1#12$1"}, {"id": 92, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "不知從何時起，“海嗣”幾乎成了我們唯一的課題。藝術、科技，我們所有面向未來的想像，都被迫擱置。", "name": "幽靈鯊"}, "figure_art": "avg_1023_ghost2_1#12$1"}, {"id": 93, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "海嗣改變了阿戈爾的許多事物。", "name": "幽靈鯊"}, "figure_art": "avg_1023_ghost2_1#12$1"}, {"id": 94, "prop": "Dialog", "attributes": {}}, {"id": 95, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {}}, {"id": 96, "prop": "Decision", "attributes": {"options": "斯卡蒂，成為深海獵人之前，你在做什麼？;幽靈鯊，成為深海獵人之前，你在做什麼？", "values": "1;2"}, "targetLine": {"option1": "line97", "option2": "line103"}}, {"id": 97, "prop": "Predicate", "attributes": {"references": "1"}, "endOfOpt": false, "targetLine": "line108"}, {"id": 98, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "m", "name": "char_263_skadi#5"}}, {"id": 99, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "我嗎？", "name": "斯卡蒂"}, "figure_art": "char_263_skadi#5"}, {"id": 100, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "我當時可是設施管理所最好的技術員，一個人就能維護一整座城市的海底燈光陣列。", "name": "斯卡蒂"}, "figure_art": "char_263_skadi#5"}, {"id": 101, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "發展規劃所給出的建議正好和我的想法差不多。我就接受了。", "name": "斯卡蒂"}, "figure_art": "char_263_skadi#5"}, {"id": 102, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "雖然一個人是孤獨了點，但偶爾逗逗那些藏在珊瑚礁裡的巨型鱗，一邊發呆一邊點亮海洋什麼的，蠻愜意的。", "name": "斯卡蒂"}, "figure_art": "char_263_skadi#5"}, {"id": 103, "prop": "Predicate", "attributes": {"references": "2"}, "endOfOpt": false, "targetLine": "line108"}, {"id": 104, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "m", "name": "avg_1023_ghost2_1#1$1"}}, {"id": 105, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "我當時還只是一個雕塑學徒。", "name": "幽靈鯊"}, "figure_art": "avg_1023_ghost2_1#1$1"}, {"id": 106, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "發展規劃所會結合實際情況，為每個公民提供建議，而且一般和我們自己的意願都能對得上。", "name": "幽靈鯊"}, "figure_art": "avg_1023_ghost2_1#1$1"}, {"id": 107, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "我想進入的領域……大概會是穹頂設計、雕塑藝術，或者舞蹈吧。", "name": "幽靈鯊"}, "figure_art": "avg_1023_ghost2_1#1$1"}, {"id": 108, "prop": "Predicate", "attributes": {"references": "1;2"}, "endOfOpt": true}, {"id": 109, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "m", "name": "avg_1023_ghost2_1#1$1"}}, {"id": 110, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "博士，凱爾希，說起來，並肩走來的這段時間，我們分享過無數情報，卻沒有分享過曾經的生活。", "name": "幽靈鯊"}, "figure_art": "avg_1023_ghost2_1#1$1"}, {"id": 111, "prop": "Dialog", "attributes": {}}, {"id": 112, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "m", "focus": "n"}}, {"id": 113, "prop": "Decision", "attributes": {"options": "因為它已經被改變了。", "values": "1"}, "targetLine": {"option1": "line114"}}, {"id": 114, "prop": "Predicate", "attributes": {"references": "1"}, "endOfOpt": false}, {"id": 115, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "m", "name": "avg_1023_ghost2_1#1$1"}}, {"id": 116, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "也是。博士，明明是帶你們參觀城市，聊起這樣沉重的話題過於不合時宜了。", "name": "幽靈鯊"}, "figure_art": "avg_1023_ghost2_1#1$1"}, {"id": 117, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "無限的波濤正懸於我們的頭頂。在面對那些令人不愉快的事情之前，博士，我們或許還來得及在此共舞一曲？", "name": "幽靈鯊"}, "figure_art": "avg_1023_ghost2_1#1$1"}, {"id": 118, "prop": "stopmusic", "attributes": {"fadetime": 2.0}}, {"id": 119, "prop": "Dialog", "attributes": {}}, {"id": 120, "prop": "Blocker", "attributes": {"a": 1.0, "r": 0.0, "g": 0.0, "b": 0.0, "fadetime": 2.0, "block": "true"}}, {"id": 121, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {}}, {"id": 122, "prop": "delay", "attributes": {"time": 1.0}}, {"id": 123, "prop": "Background", "attributes": {"image": "51_g7_consuloffice", "screenadapt": "coverall"}}, {"id": 124, "prop": "Blocker", "attributes": {"a": 0.0, "r": 0.0, "g": 0.0, "b": 0.0, "fadetime": 2.0, "block": "true"}}, {"id": 125, "prop": "playMusic", "attributes": {"intro": "$act18d3d0_intro", "key": "$act18d3d0_loop", "volume": 0.6}}, {"id": 126, "prop": "delay", "attributes": {"time": 1.0}}, {"id": 127, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "m", "name": "avg_npc_1382_1#1$1", "duration": 1.5}}, {"id": 128, "prop": "delay", "attributes": {"time": 2.0}}, {"id": 129, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "……歌蕾蒂婭。", "name": "溫柔的女性"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_1382_1#1$1"}, {"id": 130, "prop": "PlaySound", "attributes": {"key": "$d_avg_higheldshosfts", "volume": 0.7}}, {"id": 131, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"duration": 1.0}}, {"id": 132, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "斜持儀仗劍的女性緩步走來，歌蕾蒂婭下意識地把手搭上了槊柄。"}}, {"id": 133, "prop": "PlaySound", "attributes": {"key": "$d_avg_clothmovement", "volume": 0.7}}, {"id": 134, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "但對方只是將雙臂輕輕環過她的肩頭，歌蕾蒂婭嗅到神經活性劑的氣味在身邊暈開。"}}, {"id": 135, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "阿戈爾人不常以親暱的肢體接觸表達問候，歌蕾蒂婭甚至不記得母親有對自己做過這個動作。"}}, {"id": 136, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "但此刻，對方的這個動作卻顯得那麼自然。"}}, {"id": 137, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "m", "name": "avg_474_gladiia_1#1"}}, {"id": 138, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "克萊門莎執政官？", "name": "歌蕾蒂婭"}, "figure_art": "avg_474_gladiia_1#1"}, {"id": 139, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "我不記得總戰爭設計師之間有這種軍禮。", "name": "歌蕾蒂婭"}, "figure_art": "avg_474_gladiia_1#1"}, {"id": 140, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "m", "name": "avg_npc_1382_1#1$1"}}, {"id": 141, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "歌蕾蒂婭，能看到獵人們清醒地歸來，是我此行最大的收穫。", "name": "克萊門莎"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_1382_1#1$1"}, {"id": 142, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "m", "name": "avg_474_gladiia_1#1"}}, {"id": 143, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "從軍士們見到我時的失態反應來看，你們或許困擾居多。", "name": "歌蕾蒂婭"}, "figure_art": "avg_474_gladiia_1#1"}, {"id": 144, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "m", "name": "avg_npc_1382_1#9$1"}}, {"id": 145, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "斬殺“初生”的行動，令阿戈爾失去了全部的深海獵人。", "name": "克萊門莎"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_1382_1#9$1"}, {"id": 146, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "西昆妲那孩子嘗試組織了多次搜救，但“初生”死亡後，瘋狂的海嗣封鎖了那整片海域，她每一次都只能無功而返。", "name": "克萊門莎"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_1382_1#9$1"}, {"id": 147, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "m", "name": "avg_npc_1382_1#6$1"}}, {"id": 148, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "赫拉提婭——你的母親，只能向國民通報了你們的死亡。", "name": "克萊門莎"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_1382_1#6$1"}, {"id": 149, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "m", "name": "avg_npc_1382_1#2$1"}}, {"id": 150, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "但是，歌蕾蒂婭，赫拉提婭並不那麼認為。我了解她。", "name": "克萊門莎"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_1382_1#2$1"}, {"id": 151, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "m", "name": "avg_474_gladiia_1#1"}}, {"id": 152, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "或許，科學發展規劃所最優秀的執政官赫拉提婭，只是無法接受我的死亡沒能為阿戈爾解決任何問題。", "name": "歌蕾蒂婭"}, "figure_art": "avg_474_gladiia_1#1"}, {"id": 153, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "我也了解她。", "name": "歌蕾蒂婭"}, "figure_art": "avg_474_gladiia_1#1"}, {"id": 154, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "克萊門莎，我想，兩位總戰爭設計師之間的會面，主題不應該是一段扭曲的母女關係。", "name": "歌蕾蒂婭"}, "figure_art": "avg_474_gladiia_1#1"}, {"id": 155, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "m", "name": "avg_npc_1382_1#2$1"}}, {"id": 156, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "當然，歌蕾蒂婭。", "name": "克萊門莎"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_1382_1#2$1"}, {"id": 157, "prop": "Dialog", "attributes": {}}, {"id": 158, "prop": "PlaySound", "attributes": {"key": "$d_avg_higheldshosfts", "volume": 0.7}}, {"id": 159, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"duration": 1.0}}, {"id": 160, "prop": "delay", "attributes": {"time": 2.0}}, {"id": 161, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "看看這座城市。", "name": "克萊門莎"}}, {"id": 162, "prop": "Dialog", "attributes": {}}, {"id": 163, "prop": "Blocker", "attributes": {"a": 1.0, "r": 0.0, "g": 0.0, "b": 0.0, "fadetime": 2.0, "block": "true"}}, {"id": 164, "prop": "image", "attributes": {"image": "51_i02", "screenadapt": "coverall", "xScale": 1.2, "yScale": 1.2}}, {"id": 165, "prop": "ImageTween", "attributes": {"yTo": 0.0, "xScaleTo": 1.0, "yScaleTo": 1.0, "duration": 60.0, "block": "false"}}, {"id": 166, "prop": "Blocker", "attributes": {"a": 0.0, "r": 0.0, "g": 0.0, "b": 0.0, "fadetime": 2.0, "block": "false"}}, {"id": 167, "prop": "Delay", "attributes": {"time": 3.0}}, {"id": 168, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "執政官的冥思間位於城市的高處，海水此刻就懸在兩人的頭頂。"}}, {"id": 169, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "從這裡看過去，透明穹頂像是一面柔和的鏡子，將深深的混沌隔絕開來，讓阿戈爾人更好地觀照阿戈爾自身。"}}, {"id": 170, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "穹頂之下，整座城市籠罩在暗藍色的光暈裡。信標發射井高聳於城市中心，遠處，港口樞紐的艦船像是游弋的鱗群。"}}, {"id": 171, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "海水沒有顏色，唯有黑暗。彌利亞留姆就像是文明在這汪洋之中睜開的眼眸。孤獨的明亮的眼眸。", "name": "克萊門莎"}}, {"id": 172, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "曾幾何時，我們擁有無數座這樣的城市。這些點亮海洋的繁星一顆顆熄滅，成為海嗣的營養。", "name": "克萊門莎"}}, {"id": 173, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "如今，海床上散落的是那些色彩詭譎的巢穴。", "name": "克萊門莎"}}, {"id": 174, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "我不否認深海獵人計劃是一次失敗的博弈，“初生”的死並沒有遏止海嗣的進化趨勢。", "name": "歌蕾蒂婭"}}, {"id": 175, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "我需要知道阿戈爾現在的解決方案，克萊門莎，你的解決方案。", "name": "歌蕾蒂婭"}}, {"id": 176, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "什麼是“航道計劃”？", "name": "歌蕾蒂婭"}}, {"id": 177, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "歌蕾蒂婭，我無意……", "name": "克萊門莎"}}, {"id": 178, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "我也只不過是參與了另一場代價更大的博弈。", "name": "克萊門莎"}}, {"id": 179, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "“武器分級計劃”仍然只是對武器使用的嚴苛管控，其目的在於拖緩海嗣的進化。", "name": "克萊門莎"}}, {"id": 180, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "只不過這一次，我們將已有和研發中的一切武裝都列入了計劃。", "name": "克萊門莎"}}, {"id": 181, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "常規彈道武器與第Ⅰ級武器的混合應用帶來了卓越的戰果，海嗣無法理解自己為何會被身邊的海水灼傷。", "name": "克萊門莎"}}, {"id": 182, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "但它們只用一年時間就幾乎適應了這種陌生的威脅。在第十一個月，我們提前改良，應用了殺傷方式截然不同的第Ⅱ級武器。", "name": "克萊門莎"}}, {"id": 183, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "以此類推。", "name": "克萊門莎"}}, {"id": 184, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "直到海嗣的進化速度超過技術院的更新速度。", "name": "歌蕾蒂婭"}}, {"id": 185, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "嗯。我們終歸只是在爭取時間。阿戈爾投入了巨量資源用於海嗣研究，從根源上了解海嗣，才能從根源上解決海嗣。", "name": "克萊門莎"}}, {"id": 186, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "歌蕾蒂婭，你帶回來的情報很有價值。布雷奧甘在陸地上的發現從另一個側面佐證了科學院的猜測。", "name": "克萊門莎"}}, {"id": 187, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "海嗣與巨獸同源。", "name": "歌蕾蒂婭"}}, {"id": 188, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "阿戈爾是為了尋找更古老的記憶才來到陸地？", "name": "歌蕾蒂婭"}}, {"id": 189, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "不只如此。海嗣與巨獸同源，但也迥異於巨獸，它們身上有太多非自然的要素。", "name": "克萊門莎"}}, {"id": 190, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "海嗣的行為展現出了清晰的目的性，它們快速地摒棄了對海洋的依戀，開始成規模地向陸地遷徙。", "name": "克萊門莎"}}, {"id": 191, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "如果不加干預，整片大陸都成為海嗣的溫床也並非渺遠的想像。", "name": "克萊門莎"}}, {"id": 192, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "這與我們在伊比利亞的所見相符。", "name": "歌蕾蒂婭"}}, {"id": 193, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "所以，對於這個時代的阿戈爾人而言，陸地既是必須探明的真相，也是必須擔負的責任。", "name": "克萊門莎"}}, {"id": 194, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "赫拉提婭代表發展規劃所簽署了新的戰爭指令，彌利亞留姆攜帶了技術院研發的第Ⅳ級武器來到這裡。", "name": "克萊門莎"}}, {"id": 195, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "一種與以往截然不同的生物性武器，它能使目標範圍內的海嗣巢穴與幼體自主凋亡，同時將大批成體驅離目標海域。", "name": "克萊門莎"}}, {"id": 196, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "我們已經完成了對目標海域中大部分巢穴的定位，尚待投放信標的只剩下靠近伊比利亞的巢穴。", "name": "克萊門莎"}}, {"id": 197, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "待信標投放完成，武器啟動之時，我們就能久違地創造一片沒有海嗣的澄澈水域——一條連通阿戈爾本境的航道。", "name": "克萊門莎"}}, {"id": 198, "prop": "Dialog", "attributes": {}}, {"id": 199, "prop": "delay", "attributes": {"time": 2.0}}, {"id": 200, "prop": "Blocker", "attributes": {"a": 1.0, "r": 0.0, "g": 0.0, "b": 0.0, "fadetime": 2.0, "block": "true"}}, {"id": 201, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {}}, {"id": 202, "prop": "Background", "attributes": {"image": "51_g7_consuloffice", "screenadapt": "coverall"}}, {"id": 203, "prop": "image", "attributes": {}}, {"id": 204, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "left", "name": "avg_474_gladiia_1#1"}}, {"id": 205, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "right", "name": "avg_npc_1382_1#2$1"}}, {"id": 206, "prop": "Blocker", "attributes": {"a": 0.0, "r": 0.0, "g": 0.0, "b": 0.0, "fadetime": 2.0, "block": "true"}}, {"id": 207, "prop": "delay", "attributes": {"time": 1.0}}, {"id": 208, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "left", "name": "avg_474_gladiia_1#1", "focus": "l"}}, {"id": 209, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "赫拉提婭執政官不會容許自己的計劃有任何失敗的可能性。然而我所見的，卻只是海嗣重圍之下一座搖搖欲墜的危城。", "name": "歌蕾蒂婭"}}, {"id": 210, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "right", "name": "avg_npc_1382_1#2$1", "focus": "r"}}, {"id": 211, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "赫拉提婭確實對我說過，“航道計劃不會失敗”。", "name": "克萊門莎"}}, {"id": 212, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "我不知道她計算過多少種可能性，我希望我永遠都不必得知。對我來說，一直以來，這座危城就是航道計劃的全貌。", "name": "克萊門莎"}}, {"id": 213, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "right", "name": "avg_npc_1382_1#9$1", "focus": "r"}}, {"id": 214, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "但現在不是了，歌蕾蒂婭。過去的一個月產生了太多變數，我必須重新審視先前的計劃。", "name": "克萊門莎"}}, {"id": 215, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "海嗣對武器的適應性出現了爆發式的增長，它們甚至進化出了能在第Ⅲ級武器的轟擊下庇護同胞的手段。", "name": "克萊門莎"}}, {"id": 216, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "一場成功的剿滅作戰不會給海嗣留下任何向其他個體傳遞消息的機會，它們似乎以其他方式得到了啟迪。", "name": "克萊門莎"}}, {"id": 217, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "left", "name": "avg_474_gladiia_1#1", "focus": "l"}}, {"id": 218, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "海嗣針對人類產生的每一次異變，幾乎都有阿戈爾的墮落者推波助瀾。", "name": "歌蕾蒂婭"}}, {"id": 219, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "但海嗣畢竟不具備真正的智能。哪怕把實驗室裡所有的武器原型都投進海嗣巢穴，它們也不會去拆解研究。", "name": "歌蕾蒂婭"}}, {"id": 220, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "深海教會或許可以引導海嗣進攻一支軍隊、一座城市，卻很難促使它們在短時間內產生劇烈的異變。", "name": "歌蕾蒂婭"}}, {"id": 221, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "right", "name": "avg_npc_1382_1#9$1", "focus": "r"}}, {"id": 222, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "除非，海嗣不僅收到了深海教徒的訊息，還受到了另一隻“初生”的影響。", "name": "克萊門莎"}}, {"id": 223, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "left", "name": "avg_474_gladiia_1#1", "focus": "l"}}, {"id": 224, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "看來您已經讀過了那份遲來許久的作戰報告。", "name": "歌蕾蒂婭"}}, {"id": 225, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "是的，根據烏爾比安的說法，我們所斬殺的並非唯一的“初生”。", "name": "歌蕾蒂婭"}}, {"id": 226, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "right", "name": "avg_npc_1382_1#9$1", "focus": "r"}}, {"id": 227, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "歌蕾蒂婭，你們是最早進入“初生”棲所的阿戈爾人，也是最後進入那裡的阿戈爾人。", "name": "克萊門莎"}}, {"id": 228, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "如今，海嗣已經以近乎瘋狂的方式封鎖了那處遺跡。我們至今仍未找到突破的方式。", "name": "克萊門莎"}}, {"id": 229, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "而在獵人之中，烏爾比安又是滯留最久的一位，久到足夠他見證所謂的“真相”。", "name": "克萊門莎"}}, {"id": 230, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "left", "name": "avg_474_gladiia_1#5", "focus": "l"}}, {"id": 231, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "你們在猶豫是否採信他的說法。", "name": "歌蕾蒂婭"}}, {"id": 232, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "right", "name": "avg_npc_1382_1#2$1", "focus": "r"}}, {"id": 233, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "……嗯。這可能幫助阿戈爾解開海嗣謎題，也可能引領阿戈爾走向毀滅。", "name": "克萊門莎"}}, {"id": 234, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "一位憑藉海嗣殘渣苟延殘喘了幾個月的獵人居然能保持清醒，一位清醒的獵人居然甘願與海嗣同行而拒絕回歸文明。", "name": "克萊門莎"}}, {"id": 235, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "烏爾比安身上的疑點還太多，當年那場作戰中的疑點還太多。", "name": "克萊門莎"}}, {"id": 236, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "right", "name": "avg_npc_1382_1#8$1", "focus": "r"}}, {"id": 237, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "抱歉，歌蕾蒂婭，阿戈爾不得不以一場評議會來迎接獵人們的回歸。", "name": "克萊門莎"}}, {"id": 238, "prop": "stopmusic", "attributes": {"fadetime": 2.0}}, {"id": 239, "prop": "Dialog", "attributes": {}}, {"id": 240, "prop": "Blocker", "attributes": {"a": 1.0, "r": 0.0, "g": 0.0, "b": 0.0, "fadetime": 2.0, "block": "true"}}, {"id": 241, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {}}, {"id": 242, "prop": "delay", "attributes": {"time": 1.0}}, {"id": 243, "prop": "Background", "attributes": {"image": "51_g4_aegirstreet_1", "screenadapt": "coverall"}}, {"id": 244, "prop": "Blocker", "attributes": {"a": 0.0, "r": 0.0, "g": 0.0, "b": 0.0, "fadetime": 2.0, "block": "true"}}, {"id": 245, "prop": "playMusic", "attributes": {"key": "$formal_loop", "volume": 0.6}}, {"id": 246, "prop": "delay", "attributes": {"time": 1.0}}, {"id": 247, "prop": "PlaySound", "attributes": {"key": "$d_gen_walk_n", "volume": 1.0}}, {"id": 248, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "left", "name": "avg_4137_udflow_1#1$1", "duration": 1.0}}, {"id": 249, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "right", "name": "avg_npc_1391_1#1$1", "duration": 1.0}}, {"id": 250, "prop": "delay", "attributes": {"time": 2.0}}, {"id": 251, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "left", "name": "avg_4137_udflow_1#1$1", "focus": "l"}}, {"id": 252, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "我們剛剛應該已經將這裡列為了待搜查區域——", "name": "西昆妲"}}, {"id": 253, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "……伊比利亞的艾麗妮女士？", "name": "西昆妲"}}, {"id": 254, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {}}, {"id": 255, "prop": "Dialog", "attributes": {}}, {"id": 256, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "m", "name": "avg_4009_irene_1#1$1", "duration": 1.0}}, {"id": 257, "prop": "delay", "attributes": {"time": 1.5}}, {"id": 258, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "請問我該怎麼稱呼你？", "name": "艾麗妮"}, "figure_art": "avg_4009_irene_1#1$1"}, {"id": 259, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {}}, {"id": 260, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "left", "name": "avg_4137_udflow_1#1$1", "focus": "l"}}, {"id": 261, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "right", "name": "avg_npc_1391_1#1$1", "focus": "l"}}, {"id": 262, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "西昆妲，海巡隊指揮官。很遺憾昨天沒能親自迎接你們來到彌利亞留姆。", "name": "西昆妲"}}, {"id": 263, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "海巡隊正在調查一起公民失蹤的案件。我們沒有向伊比利亞方面提出協助搜查的請求，建議你盡快離開這片區域。", "name": "西昆妲"}}, {"id": 264, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {}}, {"id": 265, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "m", "name": "avg_4009_irene_1#1$1"}}, {"id": 266, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "是我本人希望能為你們提供一些協助。", "name": "艾麗妮"}}, {"id": 267, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {}}, {"id": 268, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "left", "name": "avg_4137_udflow_1#1$1", "focus": "l"}}, {"id": 269, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "right", "name": "avg_npc_1391_1#1$1", "focus": "l"}}, {"id": 270, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "感謝你的好意，但不必勞煩了。", "name": "西昆妲"}}, {"id": 271, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {}}, {"id": 272, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "m", "name": "avg_4009_irene_1#1$1"}}, {"id": 273, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "我想——", "name": "艾麗妮"}}, {"id": 274, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {}}, {"id": 275, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "left", "name": "avg_4137_udflow_1#1$1", "focus": "l"}}, {"id": 276, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "right", "name": "avg_npc_1391_1#1$1", "focus": "l"}}, {"id": 277, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "其他隊伍有消息了嗎？", "name": "西昆妲"}}, {"id": 278, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "right", "name": "avg_npc_1391_1#1$1", "focus": "r"}}, {"id": 279, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "稍等，我在調取影像。", "name": "海巡隊隊員"}}, {"id": 280, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {}}, {"id": 281, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "m", "name": "avg_4009_irene_1#2$1"}}, {"id": 282, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "長官——", "name": "艾麗妮"}}, {"id": 283, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {}}, {"id": 284, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "left", "name": "avg_4137_udflow_1#1$1", "focus": "r"}}, {"id": 285, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "right", "name": "avg_npc_1391_1#1$1", "focus": "r"}}, {"id": 286, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "港口樞紐沒有查到異常的人員動向。", "name": "海巡隊隊員"}}, {"id": 287, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "left", "name": "avg_4137_udflow_1#5$1", "focus": "l"}}, {"id": 288, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "嘖。", "name": "西昆妲"}}, {"id": 289, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "那就通知其他隊伍，去查那些已經封閉的民用閘口，也留意下城市邊緣的循環系統。", "name": "西昆妲"}}, {"id": 290, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "right", "name": "avg_npc_1391_1#1$1", "focus": "r"}}, {"id": 291, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "是。", "name": "海巡隊隊員"}}, {"id": 292, "prop": "Dialog", "attributes": {}}, {"id": 293, "prop": "PlaySound", "attributes": {"key": "$rungeneral", "volume": 0.6}}, {"id": 294, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "right", "posfrom": "0,0", "posto": "200,0", "duration": 1.0, "afrom": 1.0, "ato": 0.0}}, {"id": 295, "prop": "delay", "attributes": {"time": 2.5}}, {"id": 296, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {}}, {"id": 297, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "m", "name": "avg_4009_irene_1#2$1"}}, {"id": 298, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "你們就這麼在我面前確認情況，完全不怕洩密？", "name": "艾麗妮"}, "figure_art": "avg_4009_irene_1#2$1"}, {"id": 299, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "m", "name": "avg_4137_udflow_1#1$1"}}, {"id": 300, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "艾麗妮女士，這只是海巡隊的日常工作，沒有對你保密的必要。", "name": "西昆妲"}, "figure_art": "avg_4137_udflow_1#1$1"}, {"id": 301, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "m", "name": "avg_4009_irene_1#1$1"}}, {"id": 302, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "你們剛剛不是還讓小幫手勸人離開嗎？", "name": "艾麗妮"}, "figure_art": "avg_4009_irene_1#1$1"}, {"id": 303, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "m", "name": "avg_4137_udflow_1#1$1"}}, {"id": 304, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "那是為了避免無關人員受到不必要的傷害。", "name": "西昆妲"}, "figure_art": "avg_4137_udflow_1#1$1"}, {"id": 305, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "如果你執意留下，那麼請對自己的人身安全負責。", "name": "西昆妲"}, "figure_art": "avg_4137_udflow_1#1$1"}, {"id": 306, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "m", "name": "avg_4009_irene_1#7$1"}}, {"id": 307, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "我會——", "name": "艾麗妮"}, "figure_art": "avg_4009_irene_1#7$1"}, {"id": 308, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "m", "name": "avg_4137_udflow_1#1$1"}}, {"id": 309, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "失蹤者圖利婭，航道計劃的技術人員，負責海嗣巢穴數據的記錄與校準。", "name": "西昆妲"}, "figure_art": "avg_4137_udflow_1#1$1"}, {"id": 310, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "三十個小時前離開工作崗位，隨即失去蹤跡。", "name": "西昆妲"}, "figure_art": "avg_4137_udflow_1#1$1"}, {"id": 311, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "m", "name": "avg_4009_irene_1#7$1"}}, {"id": 312, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "有沒有可能是……深海教會？", "name": "艾麗妮"}, "figure_art": "avg_4009_irene_1#7$1"}, {"id": 313, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "m", "name": "avg_4137_udflow_1#1$1"}}, {"id": 314, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "疑點就在這裡。", "name": "西昆妲"}, "figure_art": "avg_4137_udflow_1#1$1"}, {"id": 315, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "圖利婭失蹤的這段時間，航道計劃的一應工作依然在正常運行。巢穴數據的記錄與校準當然很重要，但絕不是最關鍵的那一環。", "name": "西昆妲"}, "figure_art": "avg_4137_udflow_1#1$1"}, {"id": 316, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "如果深海教會想透過刺殺相關人員來破壞航道計劃，那他們絕不會在最緊迫的時機選擇一位最平凡的資料分析師。", "name": "西昆妲"}, "figure_art": "avg_4137_udflow_1#1$1"}, {"id": 317, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "m", "name": "avg_4137_udflow_1#3$1"}}, {"id": 318, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "除非——", "name": "西昆妲"}, "figure_art": "avg_4137_udflow_1#3$1"}, {"id": 319, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "m", "name": "avg_4137_udflow_1#5$1"}}, {"id": 320, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "圖利婭知曉了她本不該知曉的秘密。", "name": "西昆妲"}, "figure_art": "avg_4137_udflow_1#5$1"}, {"id": 321, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "我需要去一趟圖利婭的住所。", "name": "西昆妲"}, "figure_art": "avg_4137_udflow_1#5$1"}, {"id": 322, "prop": "Dialog", "attributes": {}}, {"id": 323, "prop": "PlaySound", "attributes": {"key": "$d_gen_walk_n", "volume": 1.0}}, {"id": 324, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "m", "posfrom": "0,0", "posto": "-200,0", "duration": 1.5}}, {"id": 325, "prop": "delay", "attributes": {"time": 1.0}}, {"id": 326, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "right", "name": "avg_4009_irene_1#1$1", "posfrom": "150,0", "posto": "0,0", "duration": 1.0}}, {"id": 327, "prop": "delay", "attributes": {"time": 1.5}}, {"id": 328, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "m", "name": "avg_4137_udflow_1#1$1", "focus": "m"}}, {"id": 329, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "艾麗妮女士，你很敏銳，但我仍不建議你與海巡隊同行。", "name": "西昆妲"}, "figure_art": "avg_4137_udflow_1#1$1"}, {"id": 330, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "right", "name": "avg_4009_irene_1#1$1", "focus": "r"}}, {"id": 331, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "我只是在用自己的方式調查我們共同面對的威脅，僅此而已。", "name": "艾麗妮"}}, {"id": 332, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "m", "name": "avg_4137_udflow_1#1$1", "focus": "m"}}, {"id": 333, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "……請便。", "name": "西昆妲"}, "figure_art": "avg_4137_udflow_1#1$1"}, {"id": 334, "prop": "Dialog", "attributes": {}}, {"id": 335, "prop": "Delay", "attributes": {"time": 1.0}}, {"id": 336, "prop": "Blocker", "attributes": {"a": 1.0, "r": 0.0, "g": 0.0, "b": 0.0, "fadetime": 2.0, "block": "true"}}, {"id": 337, "prop": "stopmusic", "attributes": {"fadetime": 2.0}}, {"id": 338, "prop": "Image", "attributes": {}}, {"id": 339, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {}}, {"id": 340, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": ""}}], "OPTIONTRACE": true}